 Beaux Freres Pinot Noir 2000 and Single Vineyard Pinot Noirs
Beaux Freres has just released some excellent 2000 Pinot noirs
under their "Belles Soeurs" label and we have them at reduced prices through February 25th.
Their "Shea Vineyard" 2000 Pinot noir is the best we have tried from that vineyard, and the
"Wild Thing" Pinot Noir 2000 is a great ready to drink Pinot with big rustic and robust flavors. 
Beaux Freres' signature Pinot Noir 2000 Beaux Freres Vineyard is available at less $ than the 99!
Don't miss this chance to stock up at very reasonable prices.
Read about and order the wines here:
http://www.oregongourmet.com/beauxfreres.html 
 Read about the 2000 vintage and previous vintages here:
 http://www.avalonwine.com/BeauxFreres.htm 
