GIVE EUPHORIA TRUFFLES FOR VALENTINES
If you are from Oregon, you know Euphoria Chocolate Company. Based in Eugene, they are famous for their fresh chocolate truffles, huge gobs of chocolate, fresh cream, and fruit and liquor flavors. 
Check them out here:http://www.oregongourmet.com/euphoria-chocolate-truffles.html 
 
 
